v_Tn.jpg?ver=220216\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Lead1\"><span>ためらわず<br>踏み出した一歩が、<br>グローバル開発の<br>扉を開いた</span></p>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<!-- * -->\n<li class=\"M_SE_Nav\"><a href=\"../job/members_se_yt.html\">\n<p class=\"JobMds\">SE職</p>\n<div class=\"IndexLead\">\n<p class=\"Photo\"><img src=\"../img/job/index/Thumb_Se_Yt.jpg?ver=220216\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Lead1\">複数の部門で得た<br>知識を生かし、<br>プロジェクトを<br>成功に導く</p>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<!-- * -->\n<li class=\"M_SE_Nav\"><a href=\"../job/members_se_kf.html\">\n<p class=\"JobMds\">SE職</p>\n<div class=\"IndexLead\">\n<p class=\"Photo\"><img src=\"../img/job/index/Thumb_Se_Kf.jpg?ver=220216\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Lead1\">製品を「現場の生きた<br>ツール」に。前職で<br>設計技術者だった<br>SEの想い</p>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<!-- * -->\n<li class=\"M_SE_Nav\"><a href=\"../job/members_se_st.html\">\n<p class=\"JobMds Job3\">SE職</p>\n<div class=\"IndexLead\">\n<p class=\"Photo\"><img src=\"../img/job/index/Thumb_Se_St.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Lead1\">MBSEの普及のために、<br>「新しいスタンダード」を<br>生み出す</p>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<!-- * -->\n<li class=\"M_Sales_Nav\"><a href=\"../job/members_sales_kk.html\">\n<p class=\"JobMds\">営業職</p>\n<div class=\"IndexLead\">\n<p class=\"Photo\"><img src=\"../img/job/index/Thumb_Sales_Kk.jpg?ver=220216\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Lead1\">図研に入社して気づいた<br>ソリューション営業の<br>奥深さ</p>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<!-- * -->\n<li class=\"M_Sales_Nav\"><a href=\"../job/members_sales_ha.html\">\n<p class=\"JobMds\">営業職</p>\n<div class=\"IndexLead\">\n<p class=\"Photo\"><img src=\"../img/job/index/Thumb_Sales_Ha.jpg?ver=220216\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Lead1\">訪問先の声に<br>耳を傾けながら、<br>図研の新たな歴史を刻む</p>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<!-- / .Col --></ul>\n<!-- / .IndexNav --></nav>\n\n\n</section>\n\n\n</main>\n\n\n\n<!-- #PageTop -->\n<nav id=\"PageTop\"><a href=\"#Wrapper\"><img src=\"../img/common/footer/Btn_PageTop.png?ver=220223\" alt=\"ページの先頭へ\"></a></nav>\n\n\n\n<!-- #Footer -->\n<footer id=\"Footer\">\n<div class=\"Entry\"><a href=\"../_redirect/redirect_entry.